    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Frontier for Free Today!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Frontier is a classic battle royale where you can play solo or with friends, fill your game with bots, and choose between <strong>Classic Royale</strong> or the respawn-friendly <strong>Respawn Royale</strong> mode. No matter which one you pick, the goal is simple—be the last one alive! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Loot a variety of weapons, stay inside the zone, and fight your way to victory. Matches last <strong>6-9 minutes</strong>, with continuous lobbies so you can keep playing with minimal wait. You can also use the in-game text chat to talk with friends or other players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn XP by getting kills and placing highly to level up and unlock <strong>new heroes</strong>. Heroes don't grant any competitive advantage—they are simply cosmetic and cool to have! Reach level <strong>50</strong> to unlock this season’s ultimate hero! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With <strong>challenging bots, cartoony graphics, and competitive gameplay</strong>, Frontier is perfect for casual games or even tournaments, which are hosted by the Frontier Discord community. Play today—100% free!</p>",
